      "instruction": "<p>Add the potato discs to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp – these are you <strong>potato crisps</strong></p>",
