      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>with a knob of<strong> butter </strong>in a small bowl and mix it all together – this is your<strong> garlic butter</strong></p><p>Tip: If your butter is not soft then microwave for a few secs or until soft to the touch but not melted!</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
