      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled dill cucumber</strong>, reserving the <strong>pickling liquid</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>ciabattas</strong> in half</p><p>Spread the <strong>garlic butter</strong> evenly between the insides of the ciabattas</p><p>Sandwich the <strong>drained cucumber</strong>, <strong>mustard ketchup</strong>,<strong> sliced prosciutto</strong> and<strong> grated cheese</strong> between the<strong> </strong>ciabattas</p>",
